recommendation: The CAMPTOSAR [irinotecan] label states "Individuals who are heterozygous for either the UGT1A1*28 or *6 alleles (*1/*6, *1/*28) are UGT1A1 intermediate metabolizers and may also have an increased risk of severe or life-threatening neutropenia. Published studies have shown that individuals with UGT1A1*28 and *6 alleles may be at an increased risk of severe diarrhea."  "Closely monitor patients with UGT1A1*28 or *6 alleles for neutropenia during and after treatment with CAMPTOSAR." See label for more information.
